# Live System Wiring (V4/V5 UI Restoration)

Finalize the functional restoration by implementing a live, browser-native Ledger Engine, hardening the ingestion pipeline for **Primary PDF** and **Secondary CSV** support, and ensuring 1 = 1 architectural fidelity with the original V5 "Truth Engine" aesthetics.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Primary PDF Ingestion**: The system will now prioritize PDF bank statements.
> **Forensic Reconstruction UI**: PDF uploads will trigger a specialized "Digital Reconstruction" phase to maintain the forensic accounting aesthetic.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] Ledger Engine (Restoration Port)

#### [MODIFY] [ledger.core.js](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js)
- Extend `RoboLedger` with PDF text extraction logic (via `pdf.js` or simulated forensic layer).
- Implement Smart Regex Parsers for Canadian banks (RBC, BMO, TD).
- Update [processUpload](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js#167-232) to handle file type detection and specific parsing paths.

